{
  "stem": "14613.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There is no question when people ask, how do you survive-- there's no question that luck was maybe the most important part as to how you survive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I would say, however, that in addition to the luck, it did help sometimes to have some ingenuity.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It helped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this by itself would not suffice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One of the incidents, maybe, I could say was that when we were in these camps in the Gross Rosen section, they had a number of concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was the winter, which is, there in Bavaria, a very hard winter, cold.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans camps was a gimmick, and they [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't know it was a gimmick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they said that we would like to take all the children to one camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we will summon them to factory to work so that they will be warm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It, it was quite a plausible explanation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that I would say most, if not all, the young people, children from all of these camps in Gross Rosen, volunteered.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they put us to one camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] We were about 805 children in this camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We came there, and I don't know how or what, but the grapevine started to circulate that we're not going to go to the factory to work.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we're going to go to Auschwitz to crematoria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We stayed there for a few days doing nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they send us to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's a funny thing that going to work in the cold winter, suddenly, everybody was happy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because we have noticed that if you go to work, we're not going to go back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we were happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
